        ": \"أَكْثَرُ أَهْلِ اَلْجَنَّةِ مِنَ اَلْمُسْتَضْعَفِينَ اَلنِّسَاءُ، عَلِمَ اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ ضَعْفَهُنَّ فَرَحِمَهُنَّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4628 - Ammar Al-Sabati narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) who said:\n\"The majority of the inhabitants of Paradise will be the weak women. Allah (swt), the Almighty, knew their weakness and thus had mercy on them.\""
